text: Keoney Demicoli (born 2 October 1997) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for First Division club Hibernians FC. She has been a member of the Malta women's national team. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Hibernians F.C. players
